      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――冠番組、収録前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.7000000636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……いい？　絶対に動くなよ？\nちょっとでも動いたら、あんた酷い目に遭うからね",
      "startTime": 6.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.1364404996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ううう……こんなに可愛い可愛いこころに\n一体、何をしようって言うんですかぁ",
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7530.226167099999,
          "startTime": 18.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こら、動くなって言っただろ！",
      "startTime": 19.7297742526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7297742526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "今、マスカラを塗ってるとこなんだから\n少しでも手元がブレたら、愉快な顔になるのはあんたよ",
      "startTime": 28.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "自分じゃメイクも出来ないお子様のかわりに\nやってやってるんだから、手間掛けさせるなっての",
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "よっ、kanaさんは世界一のモデル！\n着こなしも、メイクだってお手の物！！",
      "startTime": 42.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "やかましいわ。煽てられて、ほいほい言うこと聞くのは\nあのマネージャー野郎だけだっての",
      "startTime": 48.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、kanaさんは制服似合いますねぇ\nもう大人とは思えないくらい、ぴったりです",
      "startTime": 57.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}